data.description: Take a look at this exquisite 4-bed, 5-bath home with modern finishes, boasting breathtaking views including a full panorama of the majestic mountains and Pike's Peak. The property features a covered front porch, captivating jellyfish lights, and a 3-car attached garage. With a new roof installed in 2019, fresh paint, and new windows on the backside, this home exudes contemporary elegance. The main floor showcases beautiful wood floors, an office with a tray ceiling connecting to the master bedroom, and a stunning kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances including a full-size refrigerator and freezer, wine fridge, range stove, and a spacious walk-in pantry. The kitchen leads to a delightful sunroom with garage access, while adjacent to it, a formal dining space and a living room await. The living room impresses with its high ceilings, gas fireplace, surround sound, ample windows, and access to the expansive back deck overlooking the fenced backyard, complete with a pond, waterfall, landscaped gardens, and a gas fireplace. The sizable master bedroom features large windows, recessed lighting, and an attached master bath with two sinks, a tub, a spacious walk-through shower, a walk-in closet, attached laundry facilities, and porcelain tile. The fully finished basement offers a cozy ambiance with a gas fireplace, surround sound, recessed lighting, and a wet bar with a copper sink and fridge, as well as walk-out access to the backyard. Additionally, the basement accommodates two bedrooms with a connected Jack and Jill bathroom, a second laundry area, a jr suite with a tray ceiling, walk-in closet, and an attached bath featuring a walk-in shower, and even a safe room. Further amenities include two water heaters, a sprinkler system, a Generac 2.0kw home generator powered by propane, and air conditioning on the upper level, making this home a true sanctuary of comfort and style.
